name: NSImage.LoadStatus
desc: Status values for incremental image loading.

items.name: case completed
items.desc: Enough data is available to completely decompress the image.

items.name: case invalidData
items.desc: An error occurred during image decompression.

items.name: case unexpectedEOF
items.desc: Not enough data was available to fully decompress the image.

items.name: case readError
items.desc: Not enough data was available for full decompression of the image.
